videos.description: Jonathan Mulmore finds Marcus Derrickson at the top of the key for a long 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Derrickson sinks long 3-pointer for Georgetown

videos.description: Myles Powell steps in, steals the ball and then slams it down on the other end, and the Pirates' bench loves it.
videos.headline: Powell energizes Seton Hall with steal and slam

videos.description: Myles Powell forces another turnover and lays it up on the other end while drawing the foul.
videos.headline: Powell steps up with another steal-and-score
